ward Kelleher (as Edouard Dauphin)]] *[[Travis Keller]] *[[Mark Kemp]] *[[Nick Kent]] *[[Chuck Klosterman]] *[[John Kordosh]] *[[Cub Koda]] *[[Greg Kot]] *[[Sowmya Krishnamurthy]] *[[Jon Landau]] *[[Peter Lang (guitarist)|Peter Lang]] *[[Peter Laughner]] *[[Minna Lederman]] *[[Sarah Lewitinn]] *[[Paul Liberatore]] *[[Alan Light]] *[[Lotta D. Blooz]] *[[Alan Madlane (as Alan Madeleine)]] *[[Bruce Malamut]] *[[Robert Maloy]] *[[Greil Marcus]] *[[Dave Marsh]] *[[Tris McCall]] *[[Joel McIver]] *[[Legs McNeil]] *[[Richard Meltzer]] *[[John Mendelsohn (musician)|John Mendelsohn]] *[[Sia Michel]] *[[Brett Milano]] *[[Scott Miller (pop musician)|Scott Miller]] *[[Jeffrey Morgan (writer)|Jeffrey Morgan]] *[[Paul Morley]] *[[John Morthland]] *[[Charles Shaar Murray]] *[[Noel Murray]] *[[Ed Naha]] *[[Paul Nelson (critic)|Paul Nelson]] *[[Alan Niester]] *[[Mark J. Norton]] *[[Lucy O'Brien]] *[[Kim Osorio]] *[[Robert Palmer (writer)|Robert Palmer]] *[[John Peck (cartoonist)|John Peck]] (as "[[The Mad Peck]]") *[[Dusty Wright|Mark J. Petracca]] *[[Amanda Petrusich]] *[[Amy Phillips (songwriter)|Amy Phillips]] *[[Marcelo Pisarro]] *[[Ann Powers]] *[[David Quantick]] *[[Greg Prato]] *[[Nathan Rabin]] *[[Simon Reynolds]] *[[Richard Riegel]] *[[Tim Riley (music critic)|Tim Riley]] *[[Lisa Robinson]] *[[John Rockwell]] *[[Jody Rosen]] *[[Alex Ross (music critic)|Alex Ross]] *[[Kelefa Sanneh]] *[[Jon Savage]] *[[André Savetier]] *[[Ryan Schreiber]] *Bud Scoppa *[[Jane Scott (rock critic)|Jane Scott]] *[[Joel Selvin]] *[[Rob Sheffield]] *[[Ric Siegel]] *[[Sylvie Simmons]] *[[Patti Smith]] *[[Mat Snow]] *[[Bill Spooner]] *[[Marc Spitz]] *[[Alan K. Stout]] *[[Neil Strauss]] *[[John Swenson]] *[[Joe Szczechowski]] *Rob "Reef" Tewlow *[[Toure]] *[[Greg Tate]] *[[Jim Testa]] *[[Datwon Thomas]] *[[Jon Tiven]] *[[Nick Toczek]] *[[Nick Tosches]] *[[Toure]] *[[Everett True]] *[[Gregg Turner]] *[[Rob Tyner]] *[[Richie Unterberger]] *[[Penny Valentine]] *[[Clinton Walker]] *[[Richard C. Walls]] *[